        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A criatura is magically bound to an amulet. Enquanto a criatura e its amulet are on the same plane de existence, the amulet's wearer can telepathically call a criatura to travel to it, e a criatura knows the distance e direction to the amulet. Se a criatura is a até 18 m de the amulet's wearer, half de any de dano the wearer takes (round up) is transferred to a criatura.</p>",
