      "name": "Spell Storing",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A spellcaster who wears da criatura amulet can cause a criatura to store one spell de nível 4 ou lower. To do so, the wearer deve cast the spell on a criatura enquanto a até 1,5 m de it. The spell has no effect but is stored a até a criatura. Any previously stored spell is lost when a new spell is stored. A criatura can cast the spell stored com any parameters set by the original caster, requiring no spell components e using the caster's spellcasting ability. The stored spell is then lost.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
